```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>New Year Special Offer</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

.container{
text-align:center;
padding:40px;
height:100vh;
background: linear-gradient(to right,#f2994a,#d94c8a);
color:white;
}

.offer-box{
background:#ff3c00;
display:inline-block;
padding:20px 40px;
border-radius:15px;
box-shadow:0 5px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.offer-box h3{
margin:0;
font-size:18px;
}

.offer-box h1{
margin:5px;
}

.offer-box button{
padding:10px 20px;
border:none;
background:white;
color:#ff3c00;
font-weight:bold;
cursor:pointer;
border-radius:5px;
}

.products img{
width:120px;
margin:10px;
transition:transform 0.3s;
}

.products img:hover{
transform:scale(1.2);
}

.text h2{
color:#7a1fa2;
}

.discount{
color:#ffe082;
}

.card{
background:white;
color:black;
padding:10px 20px;
border:none;
border-radius:5px;
font-weight:bold;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="offer-box">
<h3>70% OFF</h3>
<h1>SPECIAL OFFER</h1>
<button onclick="shopNow()">SHOP NOW</button>
</div>

<div class="products">
<img src="https://pngimg.com/uploads/washing_machine/washing_machine_PNG15575.png">
<img src="https://pngimg.com/uploads/refrigerator/refrigerator_PNG9059.png">
<img src="https://pngimg.com/uploads/camera/camera_PNG102.png">
<img src="https://pngimg.com/uploads/headphones/headphones_PNG7644.png">
</div>

<div class="text">
<h2>BEST NEW YEAR SPECIAL OFFERS</h2>
<p>Best time to buy. Save upto <b>70% cash</b></p>

<h3 class="discount">10% INSTANT DISCOUNT</h3>
<p>with SBI Credit Cards</p>

<button class="card">SBI Card</button>
</div>

</div>

<script>

function shopNow()
{
alert("Welcome! Start shopping and get 70% OFF!");
}

</script>

</body>
</html>
```
